  "componentId": "switch",
  "variantCount": 64,
  "$samplesOnly": true,
  "$samplesNote": "3 of 64 cells. Demonstrates v0.3.0 node-tree schema on a non-Button atom. Cells chosen to exercise: active-axis layout shift (justify-content flip), SP-9 motionReduce policy=skip on toggle transition, SP-4 hardcoded $bindingStatus on track height + container width, Invalid-state ring-at-rest pattern.",
  "$cellsIncluded": [
    "size=default,active=Off,state=Default,type=Default,controlPlacement=Start",
    "size=default,active=On,state=Default,type=Default,controlPlacement=Start",
    "size=default,active=Off,state=Invalid,type=Default,controlPlacement=Start"
  ],
  "$extractionNotes": [
    "Track + thumb are first-class slots in Switch (different from Button where slots are leftIcon/rightIcon/label/kbdGroup). Switch slots = track, thumb, label, description.",
    "Active axis is layout-driven: Active=Off → track justify-content: flex-start (thumb at left); Active=On → flex-end (thumb at right). Smart-animate slides between the two endpoints. No transform/position-absolute.",
    "Auto-layout per-side padding emitted; track has px-px (1px horizontal, 0 vertical) raw — not from a spacing token at 1px.",
    "Per BUNDLE_SPEC §6.4 SP-4 + SP-4-extension v0.3.0: $bindingStatus emitted on bindable properties. Track height 18.4px = hardcoded. Container width 312px = hardcoded."
  ],

